message: The Democratic Party of JFK is very nearly dead and buried and there are next-to-no blue-collar JFK Democrats left. The Democratic Party is now extreme-left Progressive/Socialist. Jim Webb is also one of those blue-collar JFK-style Democrats and may even be the last true JFK-style Democrat leader standing. Most Democrats that I speak to are under the impression that the Democratic Party is still """"the party of JFK"""" and that is just patently untrue. The Democrat rank-and-file REALLY need to look a lot more closely at just exactly who they are associated with and supporting.
